#: ../../../style-guide.rst:682
msgid ""
"For long function declarations, it is recommended to drop each argument onto "
"its own line at the same indentation level as the function body.  The "
"closing parenthesis and opening bracket should be placed on their own line "
"as well at the same indentation level as the function declaration."
msgstr ""

